    public class CodeAuthTransitionProvider<A extends AppUser>
extends SimpleTransitionProvider<A,TransitionKey<A>>
implements AnonymousTransitionFactory<TransitionKey<A>,A>, TitleTransitionFactory<TransitionKey<A>,A>, DefaultingTransitionFactory<TransitionKey<A>,A>
    TransitionProvider to validate two factor authentication codes. This could be combined with the normal AppUserTransitionProvider but as it works anonymously its safer to keep the logic separate.
